input: what was the survival rate of patients diagnosed with hepatic dysfunction - liver transplant for a time of one year?

        CAST(SUM(CASE 
            WHEN p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive'
                 AND (p.hospitaldischargetime <= DATETIME(d.diagnosistime, '+1 year')) 
                 AND (p.hospitaldischargetime >= d.diagnosistime)
            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) 
        AS FLOAT) 
        / COUNT(*) * 100, 2
    ) AS survival_rate_percent
FROM diagnosis d
JOIN patient p ON d.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
WHERE d.diagnosisname = 'hepatic dysfunction - liver transplant'
  AND (p.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL)
  AND (p.hospitaldischargetime <= DATETIME(d.diagnosistime, '+1 year'))
  AND d.diagnosistime IS NOT NULL
;

input: among patients diagnosed with s/p cabg < 7 days, tell me the three year survival rate.
predict:
SELECT 
  ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE 
    WHEN p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' 
      AND (p.hospitaldischargetime IS NULL OR datetime(p.hospitaldischargetime, '+3 years') <= '2105-12-31 23:59:00')
      THEN 1
    ELSE 0 
  END) * 1.0 / COUNT(DISTINCT p.patientunitstayid), 2) AS three_year_survival_rate
FROM patient p
JOIN (
    SELECT d.patientunitstayid, MIN(julianday(d.diagnosistime) - julianday(pa.unitadmittime)) AS days_since_unit_admit
    FROM diagnosis d
    JOIN patient pa ON pa.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid
    WHERE d.diagnosisname LIKE '%s/p cabg%'
      AND julianday(d.diagnosistime) - julianday(pa.unitadmittime) < 7
    GROUP BY d.patientunitstayid
) eligible
ON p.patientunitstayid = eligible.patientunitstayid
WHERE p.unitadmittime IS NOT NULL
  AND p.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL
  AND p.hospitaldischargetime >= p.unitadmittime
  AND datetime(p.unitadmittime, '+3 years') <= '2105-12-31 23:59:00'
;

input: for patients diagnosed with chronic kidney disease, show me the five year survival rate.
predict:
WITH ckd_patients AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT p.patientunitstayid, p.hospitaladmittime, p.hospitaldischargetime, p.hospitaldischargestatus
    FROM patient p
    JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid
    WHERE d.diagnosisname LIKE '%chronic kidney disease%'
),
ckd_5yr_survival AS (
    SELECT
        CASE 
            WHEN hospitaldischargetime >= datetime(hospitaladmittime, '+5 years')
                 AND hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive'
            THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS survived_5yr
    FROM ckd_patients
)
SELECT

input: how many patients were diagnosed with acute respiratory failure during the same month after the treatment of cultures - peritoneal fluid, in 2105?

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT d.patientunitstayid) AS num_patients
FROM diagnosis d
JOIN (
    SELECT t.patientunitstayid, strftime('%Y-%m', t.treatmenttime) AS treat_month
    FROM treatment t
    WHERE t.treatmentname = 'cultures - peritoneal fluid'
      AND strftime('%Y', t.treatmenttime) = '2105'
) t
ON d.patientunitstayid = t.patientunitstayid
WHERE d.diagnosisname = 'acute respiratory failure'
  AND strftime('%Y-%m', d.diagnosistime) = t.treat_month
  AND d.diagnosistime > (
        SELECT MIN(t2.treatmenttime) 
        FROM treatment t2 
        WHERE t2.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid 
          AND t2.treatmentname = 'cultures - peritoneal fluid'
          AND strftime('%Y-%m', t2.treatmenttime) = t.treat_month
    )
  AND strftime('%Y', d.diagnosistime) = '2105';
